27#include <sys/cdefs.h>
28__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: i915_params.c,v 1.3 2018/08/27 04:58:23 riastradh Exp $");
29
30#include <linux/module.h>
31#include <linux/moduleparam.h>
32#include "i915_drv.h"
33
34struct i915_params i915 __read_mostly = {
35 .modeset = -1,
36 .panel_ignore_lid = 1,
37 .semaphores = -1,
38 .lvds_channel_mode = 0,
39 .panel_use_ssc = -1,
40 .vbt_sdvo_panel_type = -1,
41 .enable_rc6 = -1,
42 .enable_fbc = -1,
43 .enable_execlists = -1,
44 .enable_hangcheck = true,
45 .enable_ppgtt = -1,
46 .enable_psr = 0,
47 .preliminary_hw_support = IS_ENABLED(CONFIG_DRM_I915_PRELIMINARY_HW_SUPPORT),
48 .disable_power_well = -1,
49 .enable_ips = 1,
50 .fastboot = 0,
51 .prefault_disable = 0,
52 .load_detect_test = 0,
53 .reset = true,
54 .invert_brightness = 0,
55 .disable_display = 0,
56 .enable_cmd_parser = 1,
57 .disable_vtd_wa = 0,
58 .use_mmio_flip = 0,
59 .mmio_debug = 0,
60 .verbose_state_checks = 1,
61 .nuclear_pageflip = 0,
62 .edp_vswing = 0,
63 .enable_guc_submission = false,
64 .guc_log_level = -1,
65};
66
67module_param_named(modeset, i915.modeset, int, 0400);
68MODULE_PARM_DESC(modeset,
69 "Use kernel modesetting [KMS] (0=disable, "
70 "1=on, -1=force vga console preference [default])");
71
72module_param_named_unsafe(panel_ignore_lid, i915.panel_ignore_lid, int, 0600);
73MODULE_PARM_DESC(panel_ignore_lid,
74 "Override lid status (0=autodetect, 1=autodetect disabled [default], "
75 "-1=force lid closed, -2=force lid open)");
76
77module_param_named_unsafe(semaphores, i915.semaphores, int, 0400);
78MODULE_PARM_DESC(semaphores,
79 "Use semaphores for inter-ring sync "
80 "(default: -1 (use per-chip defaults))");
81
82module_param_named_unsafe(enable_rc6, i915.enable_rc6, int, 0400);
83MODULE_PARM_DESC(enable_rc6,
84 "Enable power-saving render C-state 6. "
85 "Different stages can be selected via bitmask values "
86 "(0 = disable; 1 = enable rc6; 2 = enable deep rc6; 4 = enable deepest rc6). "
87 "For example, 3 would enable rc6 and deep rc6, and 7 would enable everything. "
88 "default: -1 (use per-chip default)");
89
90module_param_named_unsafe(enable_fbc, i915.enable_fbc, int, 0600);
91MODULE_PARM_DESC(enable_fbc,
92 "Enable frame buffer compression for power savings "
93 "(default: -1 (use per-chip default))");
94
95module_param_named_unsafe(lvds_channel_mode, i915.lvds_channel_mode, int, 0600);
96MODULE_PARM_DESC(lvds_channel_mode,
97 "Specify LVDS channel mode "
98 "(0=probe BIOS [default], 1=single-channel, 2=dual-channel)");
99
100module_param_named_unsafe(lvds_use_ssc, i915.panel_use_ssc, int, 0600);
101MODULE_PARM_DESC(lvds_use_ssc,
102 "Use Spread Spectrum Clock with panels [LVDS/eDP] "
103 "(default: auto from VBT)");
104
105module_param_named_unsafe(vbt_sdvo_panel_type, i915.vbt_sdvo_panel_type, int, 0600);
106MODULE_PARM_DESC(vbt_sdvo_panel_type,
107 "Override/Ignore selection of SDVO panel mode in the VBT "
108 "(-2=ignore, -1=auto [default], index in VBT BIOS table)");
109
110module_param_named_unsafe(reset, i915.reset, bool, 0600);
111MODULE_PARM_DESC(reset, "Attempt GPU resets (default: true)");
112
113module_param_named_unsafe(enable_hangcheck, i915.enable_hangcheck, bool, 0644);
114MODULE_PARM_DESC(enable_hangcheck,
115 "Periodically check GPU activity for detecting hangs. "
116 "WARNING: Disabling this can cause system wide hangs. "
117 "(default: true)");
118
119module_param_named_unsafe(enable_ppgtt, i915.enable_ppgtt, int, 0400);
120MODULE_PARM_DESC(enable_ppgtt,
121 "Override PPGTT usage. "
122 "(-1=auto [default], 0=disabled, 1=aliasing, 2=full)");
123
124module_param_named_unsafe(enable_execlists, i915.enable_execlists, int, 0400);
125MODULE_PARM_DESC(enable_execlists,
126 "Override execlists usage. "
127 "(-1=auto [default], 0=disabled, 1=enabled)");
128
129module_param_named_unsafe(enable_psr, i915.enable_psr, int, 0600);
130MODULE_PARM_DESC(enable_psr, "Enable PSR (default: false)");
131
132module_param_named_unsafe(preliminary_hw_support, i915.preliminary_hw_support, int, 0600);
133MODULE_PARM_DESC(preliminary_hw_support,
134 "Enable preliminary hardware support.");
135
136module_param_named_unsafe(disable_power_well, i915.disable_power_well, int, 0600);
137MODULE_PARM_DESC(disable_power_well,
138 "Disable display power wells when possible "
139 "(-1=auto [default], 0=power wells always on, 1=power wells disabled when possible)");
140
141module_param_named_unsafe(enable_ips, i915.enable_ips, int, 0600);
142MODULE_PARM_DESC(enable_ips, "Enable IPS (default: true)");
143
144module_param_named(fastboot, i915.fastboot, bool, 0600);
145MODULE_PARM_DESC(fastboot,
146 "Try to skip unnecessary mode sets at boot time (default: false)");
147
148module_param_named_unsafe(prefault_disable, i915.prefault_disable, bool, 0600);
149MODULE_PARM_DESC(prefault_disable,
150 "Disable page prefaulting for pread/pwrite/reloc (default:false). "
151 "For developers only.");
152
153module_param_named_unsafe(load_detect_test, i915.load_detect_test, bool, 0600);
154MODULE_PARM_DESC(load_detect_test,
155 "Force-enable the VGA load detect code for testing (default:false). "
156 "For developers only.");
157
158module_param_named_unsafe(invert_brightness, i915.invert_brightness, int, 0600);
159MODULE_PARM_DESC(invert_brightness,
160 "Invert backlight brightness "
161 "(-1 force normal, 0 machine defaults, 1 force inversion), please "
162 "report PCI device ID, subsystem vendor and subsystem device ID "
163 "to dri-devel@lists.freedesktop.org, if your machine needs it. "
164 "It will then be included in an upcoming module version.");
165
166module_param_named(disable_display, i915.disable_display, bool, 0600);
167MODULE_PARM_DESC(disable_display, "Disable display (default: false)");
168
169module_param_named_unsafe(disable_vtd_wa, i915.disable_vtd_wa, bool, 0600);
170MODULE_PARM_DESC(disable_vtd_wa, "Disable all VT-d workarounds (default: false)");
171
172module_param_named_unsafe(enable_cmd_parser, i915.enable_cmd_parser, int, 0600);
173MODULE_PARM_DESC(enable_cmd_parser,
174 "Enable command parsing (1=enabled [default], 0=disabled)");
175
176module_param_named_unsafe(use_mmio_flip, i915.use_mmio_flip, int, 0600);
177MODULE_PARM_DESC(use_mmio_flip,
178 "use MMIO flips (-1=never, 0=driver discretion [default], 1=always)");
179
180module_param_named(mmio_debug, i915.mmio_debug, int, 0600);
181MODULE_PARM_DESC(mmio_debug,
182 "Enable the MMIO debug code for the first N failures (default: off). "
183 "This may negatively affect performance.");
184
185module_param_named(verbose_state_checks, i915.verbose_state_checks, bool, 0600);
186MODULE_PARM_DESC(verbose_state_checks,
187 "Enable verbose logs (ie. WARN_ON()) in case of unexpected hw state conditions.");
188
189module_param_named_unsafe(nuclear_pageflip, i915.nuclear_pageflip, bool, 0600);
190MODULE_PARM_DESC(nuclear_pageflip,
191 "Force atomic modeset functionality; asynchronous mode is not yet supported. (default: false).");
192
193/* WA to get away with the default setting in VBT for early platforms.Will be removed */
194module_param_named_unsafe(edp_vswing, i915.edp_vswing, int, 0400);
195MODULE_PARM_DESC(edp_vswing,
196 "Ignore/Override vswing pre-emph table selection from VBT "
197 "(0=use value from vbt [default], 1=low power swing(200mV),"
198 "2=default swing(400mV))");
199
200module_param_named_unsafe(enable_guc_submission, i915.enable_guc_submission, bool, 0400);
201MODULE_PARM_DESC(enable_guc_submission, "Enable GuC submission (default:false)");
202
203module_param_named(guc_log_level, i915.guc_log_level, int, 0400);
204MODULE_PARM_DESC(guc_log_level,
205 "GuC firmware logging level (-1:disabled (default), 0-3:enabled)");
206
